title: Ep.6: Steelers Vs Seahawks OT, Packers Defense, Trevon Diggs, Kyler Vs Lamar, Jets or Jags, and More
description: In todays episode we talk about the steelers thriller win in overtime vs Seattle, the packers defense and their tough road ahead, Trevon Diggs ranking among other elite corners, Kyler or Lamar starting a new franchise, and who is worse? Jets or Jags?
